comments: Dort (OKC) and Duarte (IND) make incidental foot to foot contact with each other off ball.
Craig (IND) makes contact to Bazley's (OKC) arm that affects his ability to secure the rebound.
LeVert (IND) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Bazley (OKC).
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Giddey (OKC) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the play at the basket by Holiday (IND).
Williams (OKC) makes contact with Lamb's (IND) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Muscala (OKC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Dort (OKC) engages with Lamb (IND) during the rebound and makes marginal contact that doesn't affect his ability to rebound.
Dort (OKC) makes marginal contact to LeVert's (IND) body at the end of the drive.
Sabonis (IND) brings his hand to Dort's (OKC) front during his drive and the contact is marginal.

Muscala (OKC) makes contact with Lamb's (IND) body that affects his driving shot attempt.  Lamb gathers by pinning the ball to his side with control at the time of the illegal contact and is correctly awarded continuation.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact with two hands to Bazley's (OKC) body during his drive but the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact with Bazley's (OKC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Muscala (OKC) makes marginal contact with Lamb's (IND) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Muscala (OKC) makes marginal contact with Sabonis' (IND) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Giddey (OKC) brushes Holiday's (IND) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Holiday (IND) reaches in and makes contact to Mann's (OKC) leg that affects his SQBR.
LeVert (IND) makes contact with Muscala's (OKC) arm that affects his putback shot attempt.
Bazley (OKC) commits a take foul on Holiday (IND).
Craig (IND) commits a take foul on Muscala (OKC).
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Brissett (IND).
